###Optional Extras
-both optional aspects have been implemented
1. single triangle strip is used to draw sphere and torus
2. steady frame rate of 30fps <<*** Uncomment 'LINE 5' in Makefile to compile for steady frame rate ***>>

###Application Controls 
q - escape
ctrl+f3 - lighting
ctrl+f4 - wireframe
ctrl+f5 - flat/smooth
a - axes
s - shape
c - culling
= - double tessellation
- - halve tessellation
b - double grid
v - halve grid
g - animation
l - increase number of lights

